ygData.messageBody:
I am 16th lvl Dark Elf Warrior. The Best places that I
have found for loot at this lvl is the Lavastorm Mts.
Most mobs give gems and Jewelry. But some mobs need
magic wep. Also, you can go into innothule swamp and
collect netted gloves to sell. And highhold pass is
good as well, but it is usually very crowded.
